lastCommitMessage: refactor: update delivery map components to use latitude/longitude parameters
- Changed pickupAddress and deliveryAddress parameters to pickupLatLng and deliveryLatLng in the SimpleDeliveryMap widget for clarity.
- Updated logging statements to directly reference the current location without string interpolation.
- Simplified the target location parsing logic by removing unnecessary loading states, enhancing performance and readability.
These changes improve the maintainability and clarity of the delivery map features.
